{
  "texts": [
    "However, as far as we know, more precise computational methods to infer potential GPAs is urgent in crops.",
    "To address the increasing demand, we introduced Crop-GPA, an integrated platform utilizing two computational tools for automated GPAs acquisition, storage, display, and prediction.",
    "All the curated gene and phenotypic data have been meticulously organized and represented, serving as a comprehensive repository for mapping complex GPAs.",
    "Additionally, a text mining tool based on BERT, named GPA-BERT, was proposed to extract GPAs from literature.",
    "We further extend the graph convolutional network (GCN) method to the heterogeneous graph and named it GPA-GCN for predicting potential GPAs."
  ]
}